[32m│[0m - HTML comment reveals: `<!-- TODO: Delete the testing account (test:test).  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m -->`                                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - All POST login attempts result in `400 Bad Request`, suggesting a request  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m format issue                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
